<h2 style="margin: 0 0 16px; color: #0f172a; font-size: 22px;">
  Update on your interview,
  {{candidateName}}
</h2>

<p style="margin: 0 0 16px; color: #334155; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6;">
  Thank you for taking the time to complete the interview for
  <strong>{{templateTitle}}</strong>
  at
  <strong>{{companyName}}</strong>.
</p>

<p style="margin: 0 0 16px; color: #334155; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6;">
  After careful review, the team has decided not to move forward with your
  application at this time.
</p>

<div
  style="margin: 20px 0; padding: 16px 20px; background-color: #f8fafc; border-left: 4px solid #64748b; border-radius: 4px;"
>
  <p
    style="margin: 0 0 4px; color: #475569; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600;"
  >
    Feedback from
    {{companyName}}:
  </p>
  <p
    style="margin: 0; color: #1e293b; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; white-space: pre-wrap;"
  >
    {{note}}
  </p>
</div>

<p
  style="margin: 20px 0 24px; color: #334155; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6;"
>
  We appreciate your interest and wish you the best of luck with your job
  search. You can view your interview details and AI analysis results in your
  dashboard to help with future opportunities.
</p>

<table
  role="presentation"
  cellpadding="0"
  cellspacing="0"
  style="margin: 0 auto;"
>
  <tr>
    <td>
      <a
        href="{{frontendUrl}}/candidate/dashboard"
        class="btn"
        style="display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background-color: #6366f1; color: #ffffff !important; text-decoration: none; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; border-radius: 6px;"
      >
        View Results
      </a>
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>